# Documentation site (Docusaurus) — lives on disk for local dev and is
# mounted into the docs-compose services, but is not shipped in the wheel
# and not tracked in git. Anchor to the repo root so this does NOT match
# deploy/images/docs/ (the Dockerfile for building the docs image).
/docs/


